            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meatballs are cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> green beans </strong>in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1700645025618-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1700645025618-x400.jpg",
