            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> lean pork meatballs</strong> with the <strong>brown rice </strong>and <strong>sesame greens</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>miso-mustard sauce</strong> over the meatballs</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
